      {
        "unit_id": "U0002",
        "index": 2,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "visual",
        "text": "夏日的阳光打在滨海市儿童医院的大楼上，门口人流穿梭。一辆公交车停在路边，车门打开。",
        "scene_name": "滨海市儿童医院门口·日",
        "speaker": "",
        "line_start": 13,
        "line_end": 13,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "全景",
          "performance": ""
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0003",
        "index": 3,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "visual",
        "text": "沈念歌牵着儿子沈知予从车上跳下来。她穿着一件洗得发白的白T恤，帆布鞋边缘已经磨毛。头发扎成低马尾，几缕碎发被风吹在脸上。",
        "scene_name": "滨海市儿童医院门口·日",
        "speaker": "",
        "line_start": 15,
        "line_end": 15,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "中景",
          "performance": ""
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0004",
        "index": 4,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "visual",
        "text": "沈知予——四岁半的小男孩，背带裤，口袋里揣着一包小饼干。他仰头看着医院大楼，表情认真得不像个小孩。",
        "scene_name": "滨海市儿童医院门口·日",
        "speaker": "",
        "line_start": 17,
        "line_end": 17,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "近景",
          "performance": ""
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0005",
        "index": 5,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "dialogue",
        "text": "沈知予: 妈咪，我的心脏蝴蝶今天要拍照了对不对？",
        "scene_name": "滨海市儿童医院门口·日",
        "speaker": "沈知予",
        "line_start": 19,
        "line_end": 19,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "",
          "performance": "拉了拉沈念歌的手"
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0006",
        "index": 6,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "dialogue",
        "text": "沈念歌: 对，医生叔叔要看看小蝴蝶长得好不好。拍完照妈咪带你去吃鸡腿。",
        "scene_name": "滨海市儿童医院门口·日",
        "speaker": "沈念歌",
        "line_start": 21,
        "line_end": 21,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "",
          "performance": "蹲下来，帮他整理背带"
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0007",
        "index": 7,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "dialogue",
        "text": "沈知予: 妈咪，你说爸爸会不会也喜欢吃鸡腿？",
        "scene_name": "滨海市儿童医院门口·日",
        "speaker": "沈知予",
        "line_start": 23,
        "line_end": 23,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "",
          "performance": "点头，忽然歪头"
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0008",
        "index": 8,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "visual",
        "text": "沈念歌的动作顿了一下。她的嘴角抿了抿。",
        "scene_name": "滨海市儿童医院门口·日",
        "speaker": "",
        "line_start": 25,
        "line_end": 25,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "特写",
          "performance": ""
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0009",
        "index": 9,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "dialogue",
        "text": "沈念歌: 走吧，先去挂号。",
        "scene_name": "滨海市儿童医院门口·日",
        "speaker": "沈念歌",
        "line_start": 27,
        "line_end": 27,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "",
          "performance": "站起来，牵住他的手"
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0010",
        "index": 10,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "visual",
        "text": "两人走进医院大厅。人流拥挤，取号机前排着长队。沈念歌低头看着手机上的科室导航，眉头微皱。",
        "scene_name": "滨海市儿童医院门口·日",
        "speaker": "",
        "line_start": 29,
        "line_end": 29,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "",
          "performance": ""
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0011",
        "index": 11,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "dialogue",
        "text": "沈念歌: 心内科在三楼……可是挂号单上写的是什么VIP……",
        "scene_name": "滨海市儿童医院门口·日",
        "speaker": "沈念歌",
        "line_start": 31,
        "line_end": 31,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "",
          "performance": "自言自语"
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0012",
        "index": 12,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "visual",
        "text": "沈知予挣开她的手，朝着大厅尽头一扇金色的门跑去。",
        "scene_name": "滨海市儿童医院门口·日",
        "speaker": "",
        "line_start": 33,
        "line_end": 33,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "近景",
          "performance": ""
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0013",
        "index": 13,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "dialogue",
        "text": "沈知予: 妈咪！那边的门好大好亮！走那边！",
        "scene_name": "滨海市儿童医院门口·日",
        "speaker": "沈知予",
        "line_start": 35,
        "line_end": 35,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "",
          "performance": ""
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0014",
        "index": 14,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "dialogue",
        "text": "沈念歌: 予予——别跑！",
        "scene_name": "滨海市儿童医院门口·日",
        "speaker": "沈念歌",
        "line_start": 37,
        "line_end": 37,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "",
          "performance": ""
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0015",
        "index": 15,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "visual",
        "text": "沈念歌追上去，却已经来不及——小男孩推开那扇金色大门，跑了进去。",
        "scene_name": "滨海市儿童医院门口·日",
        "speaker": "",
        "line_start": 39,
        "line_end": 39,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "",
          "performance": ""
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0016",
        "index": 16,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "music",
        "text": "音乐提示：轻快钢琴，带一丝慌乱",
        "scene_name": "滨海市儿童医院门口·日",
        "speaker": "",
        "line_start": 41,
        "line_end": 41,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "",
          "performance": ""
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0017",
        "index": 17,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "scene",
        "text": "医院VIP候诊区·日",
        "scene_name": "医院VIP候诊区·日",
        "speaker": "",
        "line_start": 47,
        "line_end": 47,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "",
          "performance": ""
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0018",
        "index": 18,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "visual",
        "text": "和外面拥挤的大厅完全不同——VIP候诊区安静得像另一个世界。柔软的真皮沙发，落地窗外是城市天际线，空气中飘着淡淡的薰衣草香。",
        "scene_name": "医院VIP候诊区·日",
        "speaker": "",
        "line_start": 49,
        "line_end": 49,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "全景",
          "performance": ""
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0019",
        "index": 19,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "visual",
        "text": "大厅深处，一个男人独自坐在角落的沙发上。深灰色定制西装，修长的双腿交叠，手里翻着一份文件。阳光从落地窗斜打进来，勾勒出他冷峻的侧脸轮廓——深邃的眉骨，挺直的鼻梁，薄抿的唇。他不看任何人，仿佛整个世界与他无关。",
        "scene_name": "医院VIP候诊区·日",
        "speaker": "",
        "line_start": 51,
        "line_end": 51,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "中景",
          "performance": ""
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0020",
        "index": 20,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "visual",
        "text": "两边的保镖和助理恭敬地站着，没有人敢靠近三米之内。这是陆景琛——陆氏集团总裁，滨海市商界最年轻也最冷酷的掌权者。",
        "scene_name": "医院VIP候诊区·日",
        "speaker": "",
        "line_start": 53,
        "line_end": 53,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "近景",
          "performance": ""
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0021",
        "index": 21,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "visual",
        "text": "大门被推开，一个小小的身影闯了进来。",
        "scene_name": "医院VIP候诊区·日",
        "speaker": "",
        "line_start": 55,
        "line_end": 55,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "",
          "performance": ""
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0022",
        "index": 22,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "visual",
        "text": "沈知予站在VIP区门口，眨巴着眼睛打量四周。他看了看真皮沙发，看了看落地窗，最后——目光定在了角落里那个男人身上。",
        "scene_name": "医院VIP候诊区·日",
        "speaker": "",
        "line_start": 57,
        "line_end": 57,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "中景",
          "performance": ""
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0023",
        "index": 23,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "visual",
        "text": "沈知予的眼睛慢慢睁大。他的嘴巴张成了一个小小的O型。",
        "scene_name": "医院VIP候诊区·日",
        "speaker": "",
        "line_start": 59,
        "line_end": 59,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "特写",
          "performance": ""
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0024",
        "index": 24,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "visual",
        "text": "时间仿佛慢了下来。小男孩歪着头，左看右看，像是在比较什么。",
        "scene_name": "医院VIP候诊区·日",
        "speaker": "",
        "line_start": 61,
        "line_end": 61,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "",
          "performance": ""
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0025",
        "index": 25,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "visual",
        "text": "陆景琛的侧脸。剑眉，深眼窝，薄唇。下颌线条冷硬如刀削。",
        "scene_name": "医院VIP候诊区·日",
        "speaker": "",
        "line_start": 63,
        "line_end": 63,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "特写",
          "performance": ""
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0026",
        "index": 26,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "visual",
        "text": "沈知予凑近大厅里的一面装饰镜子，看了看镜子里的自己——同样的剑眉，同样深的眼窝。",
        "scene_name": "医院VIP候诊区·日",
        "speaker": "",
        "line_start": 65,
        "line_end": 65,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "特写",
          "performance": ""
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0027",
        "index": 27,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "visual",
        "text": "沈知予放下手里的饼干，快步朝陆景琛走过去。",
        "scene_name": "医院VIP候诊区·日",
        "speaker": "",
        "line_start": 67,
        "line_end": 67,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "中景",
          "performance": ""
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0028",
        "index": 28,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "dialogue",
        "text": "赵一鸣: 小朋友，这里不能——",
        "scene_name": "医院VIP候诊区·日",
        "speaker": "赵一鸣",
        "line_start": 69,
        "line_end": 69,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "",
          "performance": "从旁边快步上前拦住"
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0029",
        "index": 29,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "visual",
        "text": "陆景琛抬了一下手。赵一鸣立刻退后。",
        "scene_name": "医院VIP候诊区·日",
        "speaker": "",
        "line_start": 71,
        "line_end": 71,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "",
          "performance": ""
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0030",
        "index": 30,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "visual",
        "text": "陆景琛放下文件，第一次认真看面前这个小东西。背带裤，小虎牙，一双眼睛——",
        "scene_name": "医院VIP候诊区·日",
        "speaker": "",
        "line_start": 73,
        "line_end": 73,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "近景",
          "performance": ""
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0031",
        "index": 31,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "visual",
        "text": "他的眉头微微一皱。",
        "scene_name": "医院VIP候诊区·日",
        "speaker": "",
        "line_start": 75,
        "line_end": 75,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "",
          "performance": ""
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0032",
        "index": 32,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "visual",
        "text": "那双眼睛，像极了他小时候照片里的自己。",
        "scene_name": "医院VIP候诊区·日",
        "speaker": "",
        "line_start": 77,
        "line_end": 77,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "",
          "performance": ""
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0033",
        "index": 33,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "dialogue",
        "text": "沈知予: 叔叔！",
        "scene_name": "医院VIP候诊区·日",
        "speaker": "沈知予",
        "line_start": 79,
        "line_end": 79,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "",
          "performance": "仰着头，声音清脆响亮"
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0034",
        "index": 34,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "visual",
        "text": "陆景琛没说话。",
        "scene_name": "医院VIP候诊区·日",
        "speaker": "",
        "line_start": 81,
        "line_end": 81,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "",
          "performance": ""
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0035",
        "index": 35,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "dialogue",
        "text": "沈知予: 你是不是我爸爸？",
        "scene_name": "医院VIP候诊区·日",
        "speaker": "沈知予",
        "line_start": 83,
        "line_end": 83,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "",
          "performance": "双手叉腰，认真极了"
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0036",
        "index": 36,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "visual",
        "text": "整个VIP区的空气冻住了。赵一鸣手里的咖啡差点洒了。两个保镖对视一眼。",
        "scene_name": "医院VIP候诊区·日",
        "speaker": "",
        "line_start": 85,
        "line_end": 85,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "特写",
          "performance": ""
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0037",
        "index": 37,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "visual",
        "text": "陆景琛的眼神变了。那双永远冷淡的眼睛里，罕见地闪过一丝什么。",
        "scene_name": "医院VIP候诊区·日",
        "speaker": "",
        "line_start": 87,
        "line_end": 87,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "近景",
          "performance": ""
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0038",
        "index": 38,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "music",
        "text": "音乐提示：钢琴骤停，一声单音悬在空中",
        "scene_name": "医院VIP候诊区·日",
        "speaker": "",
        "line_start": 89,
        "line_end": 89,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "",
          "performance": ""
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0039",
        "index": 39,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "scene",
        "text": "医院VIP候诊区·日",
        "scene_name": "医院VIP候诊区·日",
        "speaker": "",
        "line_start": 95,
        "line_end": 95,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "",
          "performance": ""
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0040",
        "index": 40,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "visual",
        "text": "\"予予！\"",
        "scene_name": "医院VIP候诊区·日",
        "speaker": "",
        "line_start": 97,
        "line_end": 97,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "",
          "performance": ""
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0041",
        "index": 41,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "visual",
        "text": "沈念歌冲进VIP区，脸色发白。她一眼看到儿子站在那个男人面前，心脏猛地一缩。",
        "scene_name": "医院VIP候诊区·日",
        "speaker": "",
        "line_start": 99,
        "line_end": 99,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "中景",
          "performance": ""
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0042",
        "index": 42,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "dialogue",
        "text": "沈念歌: 对不起！对不起！小孩子不懂事——",
        "scene_name": "医院VIP候诊区·日",
        "speaker": "沈念歌",
        "line_start": 101,
        "line_end": 101,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "",
          "performance": "快步上前，一把拉住予予"
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0043",
        "index": 43,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "visual",
        "text": "她弯腰准备道歉，抬起头的那一刻——",
        "scene_name": "医院VIP候诊区·日",
        "speaker": "",
        "line_start": 103,
        "line_end": 103,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "近景",
          "performance": ""
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0044",
        "index": 44,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "visual",
        "text": "四目相对。",
        "scene_name": "医院VIP候诊区·日",
        "speaker": "",
        "line_start": 105,
        "line_end": 105,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "",
          "performance": ""
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0045",
        "index": 45,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "visual",
        "text": "沈念歌瞳孔骤缩。",
        "scene_name": "医院VIP候诊区·日",
        "speaker": "",
        "line_start": 107,
        "line_end": 107,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "特写",
          "performance": ""
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0046",
        "index": 46,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "visual",
        "text": "她认识这张脸。",
        "scene_name": "医院VIP候诊区·日",
        "speaker": "",
        "line_start": 109,
        "line_end": 109,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "",
          "performance": ""
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0047",
        "index": 47,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "visual",
        "text": "怎么可能不认识？四年来她在每一个深夜都试图忘记这张脸，但它总是出现在最不该出现的地方。",
        "scene_name": "医院VIP候诊区·日",
        "speaker": "",
        "line_start": 111,
        "line_end": 111,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "",
          "performance": ""
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0048",
        "index": 48,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "visual",
        "text": "陆景琛盯着她的脸。他的目光像X光一样扫过她的五官，一秒，两秒——",
        "scene_name": "医院VIP候诊区·日",
        "speaker": "",
        "line_start": 113,
        "line_end": 113,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "",
          "performance": ""
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0049",
        "index": 49,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "dialogue",
        "text": "陆景琛: 你……",
        "scene_name": "医院VIP候诊区·日",
        "speaker": "陆景琛",
        "line_start": 115,
        "line_end": 115,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "",
          "performance": "声音低沉，不带感情"
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0050",
        "index": 50,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "visual",
        "text": "沈念歌抢先开口，声音比自己预想的更稳。",
        "scene_name": "医院VIP候诊区·日",
        "speaker": "",
        "line_start": 117,
        "line_end": 117,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "",
          "performance": ""
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0051",
        "index": 51,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "dialogue",
        "text": "沈念歌: 对不起陆总，走错了。我们马上就走。",
        "scene_name": "医院VIP候诊区·日",
        "speaker": "沈念歌",
        "line_start": 119,
        "line_end": 119,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "",
          "performance": "攥紧予予的手，微微鞠躬"
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0052",
        "index": 52,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "visual",
        "text": "她拉着予予转身就走。步伐快得像在逃。",
        "scene_name": "医院VIP候诊区·日",
        "speaker": "",
        "line_start": 121,
        "line_end": 121,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "",
          "performance": ""
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0053",
        "index": 53,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "dialogue",
        "text": "沈知予: 叔叔你不要忘了我！我长得和你一模一样！",
        "scene_name": "医院VIP候诊区·日",
        "speaker": "沈知予",
        "line_start": 123,
        "line_end": 123,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "",
          "performance": "被拖走，回头冲陆景琛喊"
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0054",
        "index": 54,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "visual",
        "text": "陆景琛坐在沙发上没动。但他放下的文件，没有再拿起来。",
        "scene_name": "医院VIP候诊区·日",
        "speaker": "",
        "line_start": 125,
        "line_end": 125,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "特写",
          "performance": ""
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0055",
        "index": 55,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "visual",
        "text": "他的目光停在沈念歌的背影上——那个瘦削的、走得很快的背影。",
        "scene_name": "医院VIP候诊区·日",
        "speaker": "",
        "line_start": 127,
        "line_end": 127,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "",
          "performance": ""
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0056",
        "index": 56,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "visual",
        "text": "赵一鸣小心翼翼凑过来。",
        "scene_name": "医院VIP候诊区·日",
        "speaker": "",
        "line_start": 129,
        "line_end": 129,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "近景",
          "performance": ""
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0057",
        "index": 57,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "dialogue",
        "text": "赵一鸣: 陆总……那个小孩说的……",
        "scene_name": "医院VIP候诊区·日",
        "speaker": "赵一鸣",
        "line_start": 131,
        "line_end": 131,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "",
          "performance": ""
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0058",
        "index": 58,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "dialogue",
        "text": "陆景琛: 查。",
        "scene_name": "医院VIP候诊区·日",
        "speaker": "陆景琛",
        "line_start": 133,
        "line_end": 133,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "",
          "performance": "声音平静，但手指微微收紧"
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0059",
        "index": 59,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "dialogue",
        "text": "赵一鸣: 查什么？",
        "scene_name": "医院VIP候诊区·日",
        "speaker": "赵一鸣",
        "line_start": 135,
        "line_end": 135,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "",
          "performance": ""
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0060",
        "index": 60,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "dialogue",
        "text": "陆景琛: 那个女人。那个孩子。全部。",
        "scene_name": "医院VIP候诊区·日",
        "speaker": "陆景琛",
        "line_start": 137,
        "line_end": 137,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "",
          "performance": ""
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0061",
        "index": 61,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "visual",
        "text": "落地窗的阳光照在他脸上，冷峻的线条下，有一丝极淡的震动。",
        "scene_name": "医院VIP候诊区·日",
        "speaker": "",
        "line_start": 139,
        "line_end": 139,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "特写",
          "performance": ""
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0062",
        "index": 62,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "visual",
        "text": "画面切到走廊里。沈念歌牵着予予快步走着，胸口起伏。",
        "scene_name": "医院VIP候诊区·日",
        "speaker": "",
        "line_start": 141,
        "line_end": 141,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "",
          "performance": ""
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0063",
        "index": 63,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "dialogue",
        "text": "沈知予: 妈咪，你认识那个叔叔吗？",
        "scene_name": "医院VIP候诊区·日",
        "speaker": "沈知予",
        "line_start": 143,
        "line_end": 143,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "",
          "performance": "仰头看她"
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0064",
        "index": 64,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "dialogue",
        "text": "沈念歌: 不认识。",
        "scene_name": "医院VIP候诊区·日",
        "speaker": "沈念歌",
        "line_start": 145,
        "line_end": 145,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "",
          "performance": "声音有些哑"
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0065",
        "index": 65,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "dialogue",
        "text": "沈知予: 可是你脸红了。",
        "scene_name": "医院VIP候诊区·日",
        "speaker": "沈知予",
        "line_start": 147,
        "line_end": 147,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "",
          "performance": "歪头"
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0066",
        "index": 66,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "visual",
        "text": "沈念歌脚步一顿，没说话。",
        "scene_name": "医院VIP候诊区·日",
        "speaker": "",
        "line_start": 149,
        "line_end": 149,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "",
          "performance": ""
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0067",
        "index": 67,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "visual",
        "text": "她低头看了一眼儿子——那张酷似陆景琛的脸。",
        "scene_name": "医院VIP候诊区·日",
        "speaker": "",
        "line_start": 151,
        "line_end": 151,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "",
          "performance": ""
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0068",
        "index": 68,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "visual",
        "text": "她的手，攥得更紧了。",
        "scene_name": "医院VIP候诊区·日",
        "speaker": "",
        "line_start": 153,
        "line_end": 153,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "",
