        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "",
          "performance": ""
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0071",
        "index": 71,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "visual",
        "text": "沈念歌抱着予予坐在医院门口的台阶上。挂号单攥在手里，已经被揉皱了。",
        "scene_name": "医院门口·日",
        "speaker": "",
        "line_start": 163,
        "line_end": 163,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "全景",
          "performance": ""
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0072",
        "index": 72,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "visual",
        "text": "予予靠在她怀里，小脑袋靠着她的肩膀。",
        "scene_name": "医院门口·日",
        "speaker": "",
        "line_start": 165,
        "line_end": 165,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "中景",
          "performance": ""
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0073",
        "index": 73,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "dialogue",
        "text": "沈知予: 妈咪，那个叔叔是不是很凶？",
        "scene_name": "医院门口·日",
        "speaker": "沈知予",
        "line_start": 167,
        "line_end": 167,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "",
          "performance": "声音闷闷的"
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0074",
        "index": 74,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "dialogue",
        "text": "沈念歌: 不凶。就是……很忙。",
        "scene_name": "医院门口·日",
        "speaker": "沈念歌",
        "line_start": 169,
        "line_end": 169,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "",
          "performance": "摸了摸他的头"
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0075",
        "index": 75,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "dialogue",
        "text": "沈知予: 那他是不是很有钱？他的衣服好亮。",
        "scene_name": "医院门口·日",
        "speaker": "沈知予",
        "line_start": 171,
        "line_end": 171,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "",
          "performance": ""
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0076",
        "index": 76,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "dialogue",
        "text": "沈念歌: 嗯，很有钱。",
        "scene_name": "医院门口·日",
        "speaker": "沈念歌",
        "line_start": 173,
        "line_end": 173,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "",
          "performance": "苦笑"
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0077",
        "index": 77,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "dialogue",
        "text": "沈知予: 那他能不能帮我们付手术费？",
        "scene_name": "医院门口·日",
        "speaker": "沈知予",
        "line_start": 175,
        "line_end": 175,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "",
          "performance": "忽然抬头，眼睛亮了"
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0078",
        "index": 78,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "visual",
        "text": "沈念歌愣住了。她张了张嘴，喉咙像被什么堵住了。",
        "scene_name": "医院门口·日",
        "speaker": "",
        "line_start": 177,
        "line_end": 177,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "特写",
          "performance": ""
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0079",
        "index": 79,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "dialogue",
        "text": "沈念歌: 予予，妈咪会想办法的。不需要任何人帮忙。",
        "scene_name": "医院门口·日",
        "speaker": "沈念歌",
        "line_start": 179,
        "line_end": 179,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "",
          "performance": "声音很轻"
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0080",
        "index": 80,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "dialogue",
        "text": "沈知予: 可是你昨晚偷偷哭了。",
        "scene_name": "医院门口·日",
        "speaker": "沈知予",
        "line_start": 181,
        "line_end": 181,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "",
          "performance": "小声"
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0081",
        "index": 81,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "visual",
        "text": "沈念歌的眼眶红了。她把脸埋进儿子的头发里。",
        "scene_name": "医院门口·日",
        "speaker": "",
        "line_start": 183,
        "line_end": 183,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "特写",
          "performance": ""
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0082",
        "index": 82,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "visual",
        "text": "画面上移——医院大楼。VIP区的落地窗。一个修长的身影站在窗后，居高临下看着门口台阶上的母子。",
        "scene_name": "医院门口·日",
        "speaker": "",
        "line_start": 185,
        "line_end": 185,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "",
          "performance": ""
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0083",
        "index": 83,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "visual",
        "text": "陆景琛的眼神，看不清是冷是热。",
        "scene_name": "医院门口·日",
        "speaker": "",
        "line_start": 187,
        "line_end": 187,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "",
          "performance": ""
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0084",
        "index": 84,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "visual",
        "text": "他拿出手机，拨了一个号。",
        "scene_name": "医院门口·日",
        "speaker": "",
        "line_start": 189,
        "line_end": 189,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "特写",
          "performance": ""
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0085",
        "index": 85,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "dialogue",
        "text": "陆景琛: 赵一鸣。那个女人叫什么名字？",
        "scene_name": "医院门口·日",
        "speaker": "陆景琛",
        "line_start": 191,
        "line_end": 191,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "",
          "performance": ""
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0086",
        "index": 86,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "visual",
        "text": "电话那头传来赵一鸣的声音——",
        "scene_name": "医院门口·日",
        "speaker": "",
        "line_start": 193,
        "line_end": 193,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "",
          "performance": ""
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0087",
        "index": 87,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "dialogue",
        "text": "赵一鸣: 沈念歌。行政部新来的文员。有一个四岁半的儿子。陆总……DNA报告要不要安排？",
        "scene_name": "医院门口·日",
        "speaker": "赵一鸣",
        "line_start": 195,
        "line_end": 195,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "",
          "performance": ""
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0088",
        "index": 88,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "visual",
        "text": "陆景琛沉默了三秒。",
        "scene_name": "医院门口·日",
        "speaker": "",
        "line_start": 197,
        "line_end": 197,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "近景",
          "performance": ""
        }
      },
      {
        "unit_id": "U0089",
        "index": 89,
        "source_type": "screen",
        "kind": "dialogue",
        "text": "陆景琛: 安排。",
        "scene_name": "医院门口·日",
        "speaker": "陆景琛",
        "line_start": 199,
        "line_end": 199,
        "metadata": {
          "shot_type": "",
          "performance": ""
        }
      },
